Package alec.is.awesome.spaceinvaders

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlienShip
    Sub-class of Entity representing an enemy spacecraft
    CanvasView
    An Android custom view that can be drawn upon and receive touch events.
    Entity
    An abstract super class for all objects that move around the screen and are controlled by the gameloop.
    GameLoop
    A class that creates a thread that executes rapidly to deal with game play.
    ImageLibrary
    A class that stores a copy of the image in RAM and allows all Entities of the same type to draw the same image.
    MainActivity
    This is the main framework of the app.
    ResourceLoader
    A helper class used to load android resources
    ShipEntity
    A sub-class of Entity that represents the player
    Shot
    Sub class of Entity.
